      "text": "键盘 : 童达琴 罗璟田",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 7.0,
      "time_str": "00:07.000",
      "text": "贝斯 : 谢宁宁",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 17.561,
      "time_str": "00:17.561",
      "text": "每次走过这间咖啡屋",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.51,
      "time_str": "00:20.510",
      "text": "忍不住慢下了脚步",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.948,
      "time_str": "00:23.948",
      "text": "你我初次相识在这里",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 27.881,
      "time_str": "00:27.881",
      "text": "揭开了相悦的序幕",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.826,
      "time_str": "00:31.826",
      "text": "今天你不再是座上客",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 35.518,
      "time_str": "00:35.518",
      "text": "我也就恢复了孤独",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 39.286,
      "time_str": "00:39.286",
      "text": "不知什么缘故使我俩",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 43.184,
      "time_str": "00:43.184",
      "text": "由情侣变成了陌路",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 47.006,
      "time_str": "00:47.006",
      "text": "芳香的咖啡飘满小屋",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 51.183,
      "time_str": "00:51.183",
      "text": "对你的情感依然如故",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 54.722,
      "time_str": "00:54.722",
      "text": "不知道何时再续前缘",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 58.468,
      "time_str": "00:58.468",
      "text": "让我把思念向你倾诉",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.878,
      "time_str": "01:04.878",
      "text": "我又走过这间咖啡屋",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 68.241,
      "time_str": "01:08.241",
      "text": "忍不住慢下了脚步",
